CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 28, 1946, pg. 3, reads: "Interested Trio - This representative threesome of the First Unitarian Church's American Unitarian Youth Group got an inkling of how the average Hill District resident lives, during a tour made Monday under the sponsorship of the Hill District People's Forum. Shown, left to right: Ross Bickley, 1140 Whiteman Street; Bill Fleck, 229 West Swissvale Avenue, and Walter Worthington, 129 West Swissvale Avenue. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ross Bickley, Bill Fleck, and Walter Worthington standing in front of woman in doorway of home with decrepit siding over clapboard, in Hill District
